- "Ownership history" refers to the sequence of owners and their corresponding purchase and sale dates for each property; 
- "Sales performance" includes the cumulative sale price, commission, and closing costs for each property over time;
- "Rental potential" is estimated based on the listing price, number of bedrooms, and square footage of each property;
- "Average recent sale price" is calculated based on properties sold between 2020 and 2021.
